dct_title_s: Tibet : ethnisch-kulturhistorische karte (für den Zeitraum von 1280 bis 1965, entspr. der Zeit der chinesischen Yüan-, Ming-, und Ch'ing-Dynastien)
dct_description_sm: Map shows ethnic minorities and ethnic Tibetans borders, monasteries, sanctuaries, and monastic traditions schools. Also pre-Buddhist religion localities. Includes portions of adjacent countries. "CH8486." Map shows location of ethnic minorities, ethnic border of Tibetans, monastic sanctuaries, and monastic traditions schools.
